<div data-role="content" style="padding: 10px;">
    {{#each reservations}}
        <div style="padding:5px; background-color:white">
            <div style="height:10px; "></div>
            <div style="font-size: x-large; color:#00C54F;">
                巴士预约成功
            </div>
            <div style="height:10px"></div>
            <div style="background-color: #EAEAEA; height: 1px"></div>
            <div style="height:15px"></div>
            {{printDateInChinese fullDate}} <span style="color:#00C54F">{{timeInHH_mm}}</span>
            <div style="height:5px;"></div>
            {{route.startStation}}  <span style="color:#00C54F">开往</span>  {{route.endStation}}
            <div style="height:5px;"></div>
            途经: {{route.middleStations}}
            <div style="height:15px;"></div>
            <div style="padding: 5px 0;font-size: larger; background-color: #F2F2F2">
                乘车地点: {{route.startStationDesc}}
            </div>
            <div style="height:15px"></div>
            车牌: {{vehicle.licenseTag}}
            <div style="height:5px;"></div>
            司机: {{vehicle.driverName}}&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="tel:{{vehicle.driverContact}}">{{vehicle.driverContact}}</a>
            <div style="height:5px;"></div>
            统一票价为{{route.price}}元
            <div style="height:5px;"></div>
            乘客：{{passenger.userName}}&nbsp;&nbsp;{{passenger.phone}}
        </div>
        <div class="btn_cancel_reservation footer_btn" style="background-color:red">
            <input type="hidden" id="reservationId" name="reservationId" value="{{id}}">
            取消预约
        </div>
        <div style="height:20px"></div>
    {{else}}
        <div style="font-size: larger; padding: 50px 0; text-align: center">
            未发现您有任何成功的车辆预约
        </div>
    {{/each}}
    <div class="div_with_title">
        <h1 class="div_title"><span style="color: #00C54F; background-color: #f9f9f9;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;温馨提示&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></h1>
        1. 请提前安排好出行时间，班车按时发车,不等候。<br>
        2. 请上车时出示此消息。 <br>
        3. 如果找不到乘车地点，请与司机联系询问。
    </div>
</div>